        </li>
        <li class="gem-c-contents-list__list-item gem-c-contents-list__list-item--dashed">
          <a class="gem-c-contents-list__link govuk-link " data-track-category="contentsClicked" data-track-action="content_item 3" data-track-label="#working-with-the-persons-health-or-care-providers" data-track-options="{"dimension29":"Working with the person’s health or care providers"}" href="#working-with-the-persons-health-or-care-providers">Working with the person’s health or care providers</a>

        </li>
        <li class="gem-c-contents-list__list-item gem-c-contents-list__list-item--dashed">
          <a class="gem-c-contents-list__link govuk-link " data-track-category="contentsClicked" data-track-action="content_item 4" data-track-label="#can-i-stop-acting-as-an-attorney-or-deputy-temporarily" data-track-options="{"dimension29":"Can I stop acting as an attorney or deputy temporarily?"}" href="#can-i-stop-acting-as-an-attorney-or-deputy-temporarily">Can I stop acting as an attorney or deputy temporarily?</a>

        </li>
        <li class="gem-c-contents-list__list-item gem-c-contents-list__list-item--dashed">
          <a class="gem-c-contents-list__link govuk-link " data-track-category="contentsClicked" data-track-action="content_item 5" data-track-label="#giving-money-to-family-or-friends" data-track-options="{"dimension29":"Giving money to family or friends"}" href="#giving-money-to-family-or-friends">Giving money to family or friends</a>

